channel.title: Project Amaze || Dungeoneering|| Webclient Ready||Summoning
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2pzmsmd.jpg[/img] Project Amaze is a Project I started way back that I worked on and on for a long period Now I'm releasing it to you guys, We have been through multiple server changes and got ripped off by some shitty Vps service. So here you guys go. Lets start out with Features!
Features
New Home
New Skilling Tab
Summoning! + Tab
Decent/Good Combat!
All Skills work! (Except Con and Hunter which aren't on there)
Dungeoneering Added with working Skill!
634 Items!
New Shops
New DonaterZone.
Cool Staffzone
2 Floors of Dungeoneering.
In Game Highscores!
+ More! I don't wanna list them all out xD.
Pictures: [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/mt4efs.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2dul6b8.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/esrt69.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/6izp92.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/334jd50.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/34gwksx.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/27x46k5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/dwt30x.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/2wf32vq.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/978rcj.jpg[/img]
Note: I'm not releasing anything big here I'm just releasing this because there needs to be more releases in this section, Its been dying lately we need to revive it and keep it going, So heres a good Project Insanity Dungeoneering Base with some cool features and a nice home Enjoy.
Links: Client (Webclient Ready): http://up.ht/mvh7MK (You have to have this client or use the erasedpkz but put our cache in it because of dungeoneering.) Source: http://up.ht/meOqNV Cache: http://up.ht/l5AFHG
Credits: Loveandpower (Some stuff off final Judgement) ErasedPkz Me Omgitsshane
[size=24pt]ENJOY[/size] [size=36pt]PLEASE COMMENT/FEEDBACK CRITICIZE WHATEVER YOU WANT :P [/size] [size=36pt]THIS SHOULD ONLY BE ON MOPAR AND RUNE SERVER AND RUNELOCUS BY OMGITSSHANE[/size]
